Module Description
This module covers all constructs like conditional, looping etc. in Shell scripting. It also covers file handling in Shell scripting. 
The module solves multiple problems using Shell scripting.

Module-level Learning Objectives
By the end of this module, you will be able to
- Write programs with conditional statements, looping constructs and files in Shell Script [Should it also be interacting with the 
  OS e.g. interacting with the directory structure or (current) processes?]
